[113.71597, "o", "\r\n  flag no ATG: ggtagtggctccggtagcggtagcggcagcgactacaagg\r\n  Match: False\r\n\r\nFLAG spans: 927 to 1011\r\n\r\nSNAP (without ATG):\r\n  Searching for: gacaaagactgcgaaatgaagcgcaccaccctggatagcc\r\n  Found at: 1008\r\n  SNAP spans: 1008 to 1554\r\n  Last 20bp: gtaagcctgggctgggttaa\r\n  Next 20bp: tgaggatcccgggaattctc\r\n"]
